Class EfsDispatcher.DispatcherStats

java.lang.Object
org.efs.dispatcher.EfsDispatcher.DispatcherStats
Enclosing class:
EfsDispatcher
public final class EfsDispatcher.DispatcherStats extends Object
Contains EfsDispatcherThread.DispatcherThreadStats for each dispatcher thread.

Note: instances are not "live" meaning this is a snapshot of dispatcher's current performance statistics and is not updated. A new instance must be acquired to get the latest statistics.

Author:
Charles W. Rapp

      public EfsDispatcherThread.DispatcherThreadStats[] dispatcherThreadStats()

    • agentReadyTimeStats

      public EfsDispatcher.AgentStats agentReadyTimeStats()
      Returns aggregated dispatcher thread statistics for agent ready time (time spent on dispatcher ready queue).

      This is a snapshot view of these statistics and is not updated after method returns. Therefore getting the latest results requires calling this method repeatedly. Care must be taken how frequently this method is called since it is not time and space optimized.

      Returns:
      aggregated agent ready time statistics.
      See Also:
      • agentRunTimeStats()
      • agentEventStats()
